tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,
review: I found both the doctors Dr.Manish and Dr.Shruti friendly and thoroughly professional. Dr Manish was always smiling and very patient in listening to my questions and answering even my silliest queries (based on little knowledge from opensource). Many a times before tooth extraction and implant, I dropped in without prior appointment and surprised to find he was studying my case which was very comforting. There was hardly any pain during the entire procedure. Also they explained post-operative criticalities and cares need to be taken. Though I was prepared for both tooth extraction and implant at same place, he advised to have tooth implant after some months due to my dental conditions. I am satisfied and It was a good experience.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,
review: Both the doctors-Dr.Swati and Dr.Manish were very friendly and ensured that the entire treatment was carried forward with high level of professionalism and patients' convenience.They were very open to answering even the silliest of queries and they made me feel at home since the first day of treatment. There was barely any pain during the entire procedure. 2 of my front teeth had to be capped hence that they worked and reworked on the capping model , till I was fully satisfied with the result and today I know if I ever have any dental issue, I have 2 doctors I can rely upon.

I have been searching for a dental implants clinic in and her east area.. I found this clinic..i set an appointment..and explained me everything I need to know about dental implants in friendly and clear manner..I cleared my all doubts.. They follow sterilization very strictly and maintain hygienic.. I am extremely satisfied with my dental treatment and laser treatment.. I sincerely recommend everyone to at least consult before finalizing your treatment to get honest opinion from true and ethical dentist...

Fantastic experience I would say.. 
I visited his clinic for 4-5 times as I had to go through root canal treatment alongwith final tooth capping. He has very nice and caring team and handles situations very well. Although he is relatively new in this field but his expertise seems very sound. 
Thanks Dr. Manish for handling my case and wish u all the very best. 
Cheers 
Amit
